Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.96,eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, look! There's Joey's picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,快看这上面有乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.96,eng,,0,0,0,,This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,还有点小激动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.55,eng,,0,0,0,,You can always spot someone who's never seen his plays before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,这显然是没看过乔伊的表演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.30,eng,,0,0,0,,Notice, no fear. No sense of impending doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,没有恐惧 对迫近的厄运毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.72,eng,,0,0,0,,The exclamation point in the title scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,标题上的感叹号吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.22,eng,,0,0,0,,It's not just Freud, it's Freud!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,显得这么有爆发力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.35,eng,,0,0,0,,Magic is about to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.35,chinese,,0,0,0,,见证奇迹的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.98,eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.98,chinese,,0,0,0,,伊娃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:30.86,eng,,0,0,0,,...we've done some excellent work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:30.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们做了不少工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:33.86,eng,,0,0,0,,And I would have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:33.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,要我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:38.16,eng,,0,0,0,,...your problem is quite clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:38.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,你的问题已经显而易见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:43.20,eng,,0,0,0,,All you want is a dinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:43.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,(歌词太黄 已不忍直视)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.46,eng,,0,0,0,,What you envy's a schwang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.00,eng,,0,0,0,,A thing through which you can tinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,(有兴趣请自行百度)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:52.88,eng,,0,0,0,,To play with or simply let hang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.40,eng,,0,0,0,,I feel violated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,我感觉被侵犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:57.32,eng,,0,0,0,,Did anybody else feel like peeling their skin off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:57.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,为了转移注意力 我都恨不得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.45,eng,,0,0,0,,...to have something else to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,撕破皮肤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.16,eng,,0,0,0,,Ross, 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,罗斯 十点钟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.20,eng,,0,0,0,,Is it? It feels like 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,才十点 我感觉都凌晨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.33,eng,,0,0,0,,No, 10:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.33,chinese,,0,0,0,,不是 十点钟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:07.06,eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:07.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:12.17,eng,,0,0,0,,There's a beautiful woman at 8, 9, 10:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:12.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,有个美女 处于八 九 十点钟方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.50,eng,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:16.76,eng,,0,0,0,,She's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:16.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:20.59,eng,,0,0,0,,She makes the women I dream about look like short, fat, bald men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:20.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,和她一比 我的梦中情人简直就是矮丑挫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.62,eng,,0,0,0,,Go over to her. She's not with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.62,chinese,,0,0,0,,去搭讪啊 她自己来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.86,eng,,0,0,0,,And what would my opening line be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,那我应该怎么开头好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:26.68,eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:26.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,不好意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:32.20,eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, she's a person. You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:32.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,不就是个女的嘛 你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.44,eng,,0,0,0,,Could she be more out of my league? Ross, back me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,完全不在我的能力范围 罗斯 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:38.44,eng,,0,0,0,,He could never get a woman like that in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:38.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,找这种妹子 钱德还早了一百万年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:44.32,eng,,0,0,0,,But you always see these beautiful women with these "nothing" guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:44.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是美女身边通常都是屌丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.58,eng,,0,0,0,,You could be one of those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以你还是有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.41,eng,,0,0,0,,-You could do that.  -You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,-没问题的  -你们确定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:50.66,eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:50.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.38,eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm even considering this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,真不相信我会这么干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.21,eng,,0,0,0,,-I'm very aware of my tongue. -Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.21,chinese,,0,0,0,,-我一向言行谨慎啊  -快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.67,eng,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.67,chinese,,0,0,0,,走你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.05,eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.08,eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.60,eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, next word would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.60,chinese,,0,0,0,,接下来应该说...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:09.85,eng,,0,0,0,,...uh, Chandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:09.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,钱德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.94,eng,,0,0,0,,Chandler is my name and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,我叫钱德 然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.73,eng,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.73,eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,你说过'嗨'了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.95,eng,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes, I did. But what I didn't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,没错 我没说过的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.24,eng,,0,0,0,,What I wanted to say was, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,我真正想说的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.66,eng,,0,0,0,,...would you like to go out with me? Thank you. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,我能约你出去吗 谢谢 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.54,eng,,0,0,0,,Chandler?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,钱德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.12,eng,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,明星出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:36.42,eng,,0,0,0,,-I didn't know you could dance!  -You were in a play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:36.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,-我都不知道你会跳舞啊  -你是主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.09,eng,,0,0,0,,What'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,你们觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.13,eng,,0,0,0,,-I didn't know you could dance!  -You were in a play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,-我都不知道你会跳舞啊  -你是主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.01,eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, it wasn't that bad. I was the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,拜托 没这么烂吧 我可是领唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:48.47,eng,,0,0,0,,It was better than the troll thing. At least you got to see my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:48.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,这比轮唱好多了 至少可以看到我的脑袋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.81,eng,,0,0,0,,-You're right.  -We saw your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,-没错  -确实看见你脑袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.56,eng,,0,0,0,,She said yes! She said yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,她同意了 同意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.36,eng,,0,0,0,,Awful play, man! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,演的烂死了 靠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:03.57,eng,,0,0,0,,Her name's Aurora. She's Italian and she pronounces my name "Chandler."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:03.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,她叫奥萝拉 意大利人 念我名字都念得这么性感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.78,eng,,0,0,0,,I like that better. The usher gave me this to give to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.78,chinese,,0,0,0,,这么念挺不错 对了 招待让我把这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.08,eng,,0,0,0,,-What is it?  -The Estelle Leonard Talent Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,-啥啊  -艾斯黛尔经纪公司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.12,eng,,0,0,0,,An agency left me its card. Maybe they wanna sign me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,有经纪人给我留名片啦 没准是想签我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.50,eng,,0,0,0,,Based on this play?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,就因为这个表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.13,eng,,0,0,0,,Based on this play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,完全是因为这次表演嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.18,eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.18,chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.39,eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.39,chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿 钱德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.02,eng,,0,0,0,,No, because this line is passion, and this is just a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.02,chinese,,0,0,0,,这条才是感情线 这条啥都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:40.07,eng,,0,0,0,,I've been here seven seconds, and you haven't asked me how my date went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:40.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,我都坐这7秒钟了 没人问我约会的咋样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.74,eng,,0,0,0,,How was your date, Chandler?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,约会怎么样啊 钱德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.20,eng,,0,0,0,,It was unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,极端犀利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:49.03,eng,,0,0,0,,I've never met anyone like her. She's had the most amazing life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:49.03,chinese,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过生活这么精彩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.91,eng,,0,0,0,,She was in the Israeli army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,她曾经在以色列参军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.20,eng,,0,0,0,,None of the bullets hit the engine block...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,还好没有子弹打中引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.83,eng,,0,0,0,,...so we made it to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.83,chinese,,0,0,0,,于是我们到了边境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.96,eng,,0,0,0,,But just barely and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是挺危险 然后我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.96,eng,,0,0,0,,I've been talking about myself all night long. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,我整晚都在说我自己 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.26,eng,,0,0,0,,What about you? Tell me your stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,给我讲讲你的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.34,eng,,0,0,0,,All right, once...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧 有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:10.30,eng,,0,0,0,,...once I got on the subway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:10.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,有一次我坐地铁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.18,eng,,0,0,0,,And it was at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.18,chinese,,0,0,0,,在晚上坐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:15.06,eng,,0,0,0,,...and I rode it all the way to Brooklyn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:15.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后一直坐到了布鲁克林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.77,eng,,0,0,0,,...just for the hell of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.77,chinese,,0,0,0,,纯属是闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.19,eng,,0,0,0,,We talked till 2. It was this perfect evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们一直聊到两点 完美的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.36,eng,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,其实也不太完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.94,eng,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, we realized we were in Yemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,突然 我们意识到那里是也门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.95,eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, so "we" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们都是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.07,eng,,0,0,0,,"We" is me and Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,是我和瑞克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.74,eng,,0,0,0,,-Who's Rick? -Who's Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,-瑞克是谁  -瑞克是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.00,eng,,0,0,0,,My husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.83,eng,,0,0,0,,-Oh, so you're divorced?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.83,chinese,,0,0,0,,-你离婚了  -没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.31,eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. So you're widowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那你丈夫去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.14,eng,,0,0,0,,Hopefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.14,chinese,,0,0,0,,希望是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.72,eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm still married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,没有 我们还是夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:52.80,eng,,0,0,0,,So how would your husband feel about you sitting here with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:52.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,那我挺好奇你丈夫的想法 你和我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.47,eng,,0,0,0,,...sliding your foot so far up my leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,把你的脚伸到我腿上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.23,eng,,0,0,0,,...you can count the change in my pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.23,chinese,,0,0,0,,都能数清我口袋里的零钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.19,eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.40,eng,,0,0,0,,I imagine he'd be okay with you because he's okay with Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,我猜他不会介意 因为他都没介意我和伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.36,eng,,0,0,0,,Ethan? There's an Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,伊森 还有个伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.45,eng,,0,0,0,,Ethan is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,伊森是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.91,eng,,0,0,0,,...boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.33,eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.33,chinese,,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:19.33,eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh, what kind of relationship do you imagine us having...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:19.33,chinese,,0,0,0,,额 那咱俩目前这算是什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.13,eng,,0,0,0,,...if you already have a husband and a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,既然你已经有了丈夫和男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.55,eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose, mainly sexual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,主要是..性关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.80,eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,真替你感到遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.30,eng,,0,0,0,,What not work out? I'm seeing her again on Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,遗憾啥 我和她约了周四见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.24,eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you listen to the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,你没听明白刚才的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.35,eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you listen to the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.35,chinese,,0,0,0,,是你没明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:43.27,eng,,0,0,0,,How could you get involved with a woman like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:43.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,你怎么还能和这样的女人搞在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.94,eng,,0,0,0,,I had trouble with it at first, but I get all the good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,我开始也很纠结 不过后来我看开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.57,eng,,0,0,0,,All the fun, all the talking, all the sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,和她约会既有趣 有的聊 还能上床
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.45,eng,,0,0,0,,...and no responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,而且还没责任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.87,eng,,0,0,0,,This is every guy's fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.87,chinese,,0,0,0,,这是每个男人的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.62,eng,,0,0,0,,That is not true. Ross, is this your fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.62,chinese,,0,0,0,,扯呢吧 罗斯 这是你的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.58,eng,,0,0,0,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,必须不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.71,eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,没错 是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:09.13,eng,,0,0,0,,You'd go out with someone else who's going out with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:09.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,你们就不介意约会的女生有其他男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.47,eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,我忍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.72,eng,,0,0,0,,Good for you. Joey
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,就你还靠谱点 乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.18,eng,,0,0,0,,When I'm with a woman, I need to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.18,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我和一个女的约会 我必须确定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.26,eng,,0,0,0,,...that I'm going out with more people than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,我的备胎比她更多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:18.85,eng,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:18.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,其实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.06,eng,,0,0,0,,...monogamy can be a tricky concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,一夫一妻制是个挺复杂的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.60,eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, anthropologically...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.60,chinese,,0,0,0,,从人类学的角度...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.53,eng,,0,0,0,,Fine. Now you'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.53,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们失去了学习知识的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.36,eng,,0,0,0,,We're kidding. Tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,开玩笑呢 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.20,eng,,0,0,0,,We wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:36.20,eng,,0,0,0,,All right. There's a theory put forth by Richard Leakey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:36.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧 理查德里奇有一个理论说...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.51,eng,,0,0,0,,Are we greeting each other this way now? I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.51,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在流行这么打招呼吗 我还挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.84,eng,,0,0,0,,Look! I cleaned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.84,chinese,,0,0,0,,快看 我打扫了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.30,eng,,0,0,0,,I did the windows. I did the floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,擦了窗户 擦了地板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:08:00.10,eng,,0,0,0,,I used all the attachments on the vacuum except for that round one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:08:00.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,吸尘器上的所有部件我都用了 除了一个圆形的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.48,eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.48,chinese,,0,0,0,,我不知道是干啥用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.00,eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows, and we're not supposed to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,没人知道 而且没人敢问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.31,eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,你们觉得咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.27,eng,,0,0,0,,-It's very clean.  -Really, it looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,-挺干净的  -相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:16.36,eng,,0,0,0,,Oh. Heh. I see you moved the green ottoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:16.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,噢 你把绿色软椅放到这了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.79,eng,,0,0,0,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,为啥放这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.71,eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I thought it looked better there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得放到那挺好看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.25,eng,,0,0,0,,And also, it's an extra seat around the coffee table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,而且这样就多出来了一个座位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.80,eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,挺有新意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.47,eng,,0,0,0,,But you know what? Just for fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,不过...我纯属娱乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:39.43,eng,,0,0,0,,...let's see what it looked like in the old spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:39.43,chinese,,0,0,0,,咱们看看以前的摆法怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.93,eng,,0,0,0,,Just to compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,比较一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.64,eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.73,eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks good there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,放在这也挺好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.31,eng,,0,0,0,,Let's leave it there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,那就在这放一阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.15,eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you tried to move the green ottoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.15,chinese,,0,0,0,,你居然敢移动那个软椅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.49,eng,,0,0,0,,Thank God you didn't fan out the magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.49,chinese,,0,0,0,,还好你没摊开那些杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.57,eng,,0,0,0,,She'll scratch your eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,要不她得把你眼睛挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.66,eng,,0,0,0,,You guys, I am not that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿 我没那么偏执吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.12,eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you are. Monica
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,没错 你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.04,eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, I lived with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,还记得我住这里的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.71,eng,,0,0,0,,You were a little, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,你就像这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.42,eng,,0,0,0,,That is so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:15.47,eng,,0,0,0,,When we were kids, yours was the only Raggedy Ann doll that wasn't raggedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:15.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,咱们小的时候 只有你的破烂娃娃是不破的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.93,eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, so I'm responsible. I'm organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧 我负责任 有条理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.97,eng,,0,0,0,,But, hey, I can be a kook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,我也可以很邋遢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.44,eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you madcap gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧 狂野美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.36,eng,,0,0,0,,Try to imagine this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,试想一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:34.28,eng,,0,0,0,,The phone bill arrives, but you don't pay it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:34.28,chinese,,0,0,0,,电话单到了 但是你却没有马上去交费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.11,eng,,0,0,0,,-Why not? -Because you're a kook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,-为啥  -因为你邋遢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.99,eng,,0,0,0,,Instead, you wait until they send you a notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,而且你一直拖到他们提醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.12,eng,,0,0,0,,I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.29,eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, then you let me go grocery shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,试试这个 你让我去杂货店买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.36,eng,,0,0,0,,...and I buy laundry detergent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,我买了洗衣液
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.96,eng,,0,0,0,,But it's not the one with the easy-pour spout.
