Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,-我得走了  -她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:19.20,eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. He'll be waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:19.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉 他在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.04,eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you talked to Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,我以为你和瑞克说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.17,eng,,0,0,0,,It's not Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,不是瑞克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.50,eng,,0,0,0,,Ethan? He gets the whole day with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,伊森已经占了你一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.42,eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,不是 是安德鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.01,eng,,0,0,0,,I know there'll be many moments...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道以后我肯定会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.56,eng,,0,0,0,,...when I'll regret asking the following question, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,经常后悔我问了这个问题 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.81,eng,,0,0,0,,And Andrew is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,安德鲁是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.14,eng,,0,0,0,,He's... new.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.14,chinese,,0,0,0,,他是 新欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:48.65,eng,,0,0,0,,So you're not completely fulfilled by Rick, Ethan and myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:48.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以瑞克 伊森再加上我 都不能满足你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.32,eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's not exactly what I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,不是 我并没有这么觉得...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.36,eng,,0,0,0,,Most women would kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,无数女同胞都会被
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.66,eng,,0,0,0,,...for three guys like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们三个秒杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.41,eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,那你想要怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.16,eng,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.21,eng,,0,0,0,,-You have me. -No, no. Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.21,chinese,,0,0,0,,-你有我啊  -不是 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.62,eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.62,chinese,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.71,eng,,0,0,0,,Lose the other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,把其他人都甩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.46,eng,,0,0,0,,Like, all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.46,chinese,,0,0,0,,全都甩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.13,eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're great together. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们在一起很棒 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.51,eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't we just have what we have now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.51,chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么不能维持现状呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:19.06,eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't we just talk, laugh and make love...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:19.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,只是聊天 大笑 做爱...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.10,eng,,0,0,0,,...without feeling obligated to one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,而丝毫不用担心被绑住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:26.10,eng,,0,0,0,,Up until tonight, I thought that's what you wanted too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:26.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,今晚之前我以为你也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.23,eng,,0,0,0,,Well, part of me wants that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.23,chinese,,0,0,0,,一部分的我想要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.65,eng,,0,0,0,,...but it's like I'm two guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我身体里有两个小人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.86,eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, one guy's saying, "Shut up! This is great!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,一个说'闭嘴 这样多好啊'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.74,eng,,0,0,0,,But there's this other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是另外一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.95,eng,,0,0,0,,It's the guy who wells up every time the Grinch's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,他每次都会跳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.04,eng,,0,0,0,,...grows three sizes and breaks that measuring device.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,阻止我越陷越深
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.84,eng,,0,0,0,,He's saying, you know, "This is too hard. Get out, get out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.84,chinese,,0,0,0,,他一直说'这太扭曲了 快离开她'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.55,eng,,0,0,0,,So which one of the two guys will you listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,那你会听谁的建议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.34,eng,,0,0,0,,I have to listen to both. They don't let each other finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,都听 因为他们总是不让对方说完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.05,eng,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.02,eng,,0,0,0,,The second guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.02,chinese,,0,0,0,,第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:07.90,eng,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:07.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.90,eng,,0,0,0,,Call me if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,改变主意了就打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.79,eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, the first guy runs the lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉 第一个小人动的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:42.51,eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it this way. You dumped her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:42.51,chinese,,0,0,0,,换个角度看 是你甩的她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.14,eng,,0,0,0,,Right? I mean, this woman was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.14,chinese,,0,0,0,,对吧 这个女的长得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.98,eng,,0,0,0,,...unbelievably sexy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.98,chinese,,0,0,0,,异常的火辣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.56,eng,,0,0,0,,...and beautiful, intelligent, unattainable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,美丽 聪明 可望而不可即
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.78,eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me why you did this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.78,chinese,,0,0,0,,告诉我你为啥分手来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.61,eng,,0,0,0,,Movie star!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,大明星来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:03.49,eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the guy who plays the butt in the new Al Pacino movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:03.49,chinese,,0,0,0,,你不是演艾尔·帕西诺屁股的影星嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:06.70,eng,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:06.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.54,eng,,0,0,0,,No? What happened, big guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,不是吗 发生什么了 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.21,eng,,0,0,0,,Big guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.21,chinese,,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.59,eng,,0,0,0,,It felt like a "big guy" moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得这应该是个'猛男时刻'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.59,eng,,0,0,0,,I got fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,我被炒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.76,eng,,0,0,0,,They said I acted too much with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,他们说我的表演太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.43,eng,,0,0,0,,I told everybody about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.43,chinese,,0,0,0,,所有人都知道我要演出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.60,eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody will be expecting to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.60,chinese,,0,0,0,,他们还都等着看我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.39,eng,,0,0,0,,You know what? No one will be able to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.39,chinese,,0,0,0,,别担心 反正他们也认不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.27,eng,,0,0,0,,My mom will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,我妈妈能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.28,eng,,0,0,0,,There's something so sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.28,chinese,,0,0,0,,真是令人既感动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.74,eng,,0,0,0,,...and disturbing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,又反胃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:42.95,eng,,0,0,0,,I've done nothing but crappy plays for six years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:42.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,我这六年除了演烂片没干别的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.20,eng,,0,0,0,,...and I finally get my shot, and I blow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,终于有个机会翻身 我却搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:48.16,eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe this wasn't your shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:48.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,也许这并不是真正的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:52.92,eng,,0,0,0,,I think when it's your shot, you know it's your shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:52.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,没错 当机会来临的时候 你会清晰的感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.05,eng,,0,0,0,,Did it feel like your shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,你有这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.05,eng,,0,0,0,,Hard to tell. I was naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,难说 毕竟是裸体拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.88,eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think this was your shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.88,chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为这不是你的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.39,eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even think you just get one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.39,chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得你翻身的机会还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.97,eng,,0,0,0,,I really believe big things are gonna happen for you. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我相信你以后会飞黄腾达 一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:12.10,eng,,0,0,0,,You've gotta keep thinking about the day that some kid will go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:12.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,总有一天会有一个小孩子大喊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:15.98,eng,,0,0,0,,..."I got the part! I'm gonna be Joey Tribbiani's ass!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:15.98,chinese,,0,0,0,,'我拿到这个角色了 演乔伊·崔比昂尼的屁股'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.90,eng,,0,0,0,,You think? That's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,真的吗 你太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.70,eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,走一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.83,eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Joey. I'm gonna go to bed, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.83,chinese,,0,0,0,,开心点 乔伊 我去睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.12,eng,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.71,eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna leave your shoes out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,你打算把鞋留在那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.18,eng,,0,0,0,,Really? Just casually strewn about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.18,chinese,,0,0,0,,真的吗 就这么随手一扔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.68,eng,,0,0,0,,...in that reckless, haphazard manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,简单随意的撇在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.31,eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. I'll get them tomorrow. Or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,没关系 明天再说吧 没准就一直放那了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.23,eng,,0,0,0,,Whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.23,chinese,,0,0,0,,不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.65,eng,,0,0,0,,She is a kook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,她还真能邋遢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:17.46,eng,,0,0,0,,If it bothers you that much, just go out and get the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:17.46,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果这么在意 出去把鞋捡起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.63,eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.63,chinese,,0,0,0,,别 千万别捡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.30,eng,,0,0,0,,This is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,这太二了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.64,eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have to prove anything. I'm gonna go get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,我又不用证明什么 我要去捡起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.18,eng,,0,0,0,,But then everyone will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.18,chinese,,0,0,0,,可是这样所有人就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:34.98,eng,,0,0,0,,Unless I get them, and then wake up really early and put them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:34.98,chinese,,0,0,0,,除非我捡起来 然后明天早起再放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.94,eng,,0,0,0,,I need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,谁来帮帮我啊
